name: mind-util
author: iarkn
description:
A client-side utility mod. Contains useful (probably) features such as
  - console
  - unit spawner
  - entity display
  - and more...

Press F9 to access the utilities menu on desktop. On mobile, tap the button with a stack icon once you have loaded a world.

For more information, please visit <https://github.com/iarkn/mind-util/wiki>.
